# UV Pip-Compatible Commands

## Package Installation
Install packages using pip-compatible commands:
```bash
uv pip install {package}          # Install latest version
uv pip install "{package}<1.0.0"  # Install with version constraint
uv pip install --upgrade {package} # Upgrade existing package
```

## Package Removal
Remove installed packages:
```bash
uv pip uninstall {package}        # Remove a package
```

## Environment Synchronization
Sync environment from requirements:
```bash
uv pip sync requirements.txt      # Sync from requirements file
```

## Requirements Management
Generate requirements files:
```bash
uv pip compile pyproject.toml -o requirements.txt  # Generate requirements.txt
```

## VCS Installation
Install from version control:
```bash
uv pip install "package @ git+https://github.com/user/repo.git"  # Install from Git
```
